metadata.description:
INSPIRATION | She fell asleep shortly after. 
- Diptych / second part

An emotional scene fragrant with gentle eroticism.
Dark bedding. All passion and tenderness. Sparks. Explosions. Breaths. 
By now everything around you is drowning in half-sleep. Only you know what to think about it.

Intense, dark background colors, highlights the power of emotions.
The painting can be part of a diptych - or an independent work of art.
Oil on canvas, technique of intense, strong brushstrokes.

ONE ORIGINAL | Image signed on front and back by EDigitized with high quality.
Authentication in the blockchain - the only NFT minted only at uni.decnetala-art.com

The image cut into 100 pieces each is of high quality. Any collector can become the owner of one or more pieces of this work of art. Collectors are free to value purchased pieces at will and trade pieces of this painting among themselves.

Awards:
Collecting more pieces of the contract pays a reward. The owner of the wallet who collects the entire painting in one wallet will receive a prize of 80% of the price, and a real oil painting painted on canvas.K.
Author's Certificate of Authenticity will be included.
